In an interview with Sports Illustrated Giroud said: 'I think he could put more aggressiveness in his game.

'I know he's not a strong fellow, but he's a fantastic footballer. 

'Technically, he's amazing, and he sees everything before the other players. He needs to play more, but he has fantastic quality.'

